    </div>
    <h2 class="home-about-heading" id="aboutHeading">Hi 👋 I'm Kathryne Mueller.</h2>

    <!-- Professional content -->
    <div class="about-panel about-panel--work active" id="aboutWork">
      <p class="home-about-body">Over the past 10 years I've led end-to-end product design across a variety of industries, like health, energy, retail, automotive, and telecoms. I've delivered high-impact work for leading global brands and early-stage startups alike, and adapted quickly to new domains and challenges.</p>
      <p class="home-about-body" style="margin-top: 20px;">With a degree in Graphic &amp; Communication Design from Leeds University, I spent time earlier in my career in digital content, media, and marketing, before feeling a strong pull back to creating. What I love about UX is fundamentally what it's always been about - problem solving. Understanding what people actually <em>need</em>, and designing something that genuinely works for them.</p>
      <p class="home-about-body" style="margin-top: 20px;">I'm excited to bring that curiosity somewhere new, so I am currently open to permanent and freelance opportunities.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Personal content -->
    <div class="about-panel about-panel--personal" id="aboutPersonal">
      <p class="home-about-body">Free time is rare, but when I get it I try to make it count! I'm usually outdoors or staying active. I've recently got into kickboxing, which I love 🥊</p>
      <p class="home-about-body" style="margin-top: 20px;">I like trying to learn something new, whether that's a craft or a recipe. I've been baking a lot lately and I'm pretty proud of my Bavarian pretzel 🥨</p>
      <p class="home-about-body" style="margin-top: 20px;">I also speak a pretty good level of German now, after about a decade of learning, which comes in handy when I'm in the Alps, one of my favourite places in the world <span style="white-space: nowrap;">🏔️</span></p>
      <p class="home-about-body" style="margin-top: 20px;">Family is a big part of my life, and we spend time exploring the River Thames beauty spots on weekends near our hometown in Berkshire. 🌿</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  </div>
</section>

<script>
(function() {
  const toggle = document.getElementById('aboutToggle');
  const flipCard = document.getElementById('aboutFlipCard');
  const workPanel = document.getElementById('aboutWork');
  const personalPanel = document.getElementById('aboutPersonal');
  const heading = document.getElementById('aboutHeading');
  if (!toggle) return;

  toggle.querySelectorAll('.about-toggle-btn').forEach(btn => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const mode = btn.dataset.mode;
      toggle.querySelectorAll('.about-toggle-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
      btn.classList.add('active');

      if (mode === 'personal') {
        flipCard.classList.add('flipped');
        workPanel.classList.remove('active');
        personalPanel.classList.add('active');
        function updateArrow() {
          const isStacked = window.getComputedStyle(document.querySelector('.home-about-inner')).flexDirection === 'column';
          heading.textContent = (isStacked ? '↑' : '←') + ' You\'ll find me here';
        }
        updateArrow();
        window._aboutArrowListener = updateArrow;
        window.addEventListener('resize', updateArrow);
        heading.style.fontStyle = 'normal';
      } else {
        flipCard.classList.remove('flipped');
        workPanel.classList.add('active');
        personalPanel.classList.remove('active');
        heading.textContent = 'Hi 👋 I\'m Kathryne Mueller.';
        heading.style.fontStyle = '';
      }
    });
  });
})();
</script>

